### 1. Create a Draft Event (Allows missing fields for draft mode)
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/create
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": true,
  "eventTitle": "Tech Conference 2026 (Draft)",
  "notes": "Draft setup with basic details"
}

### 2. Create a Fully Published Event (All required fields provided)
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/create
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json  

{
  "isDraft": false,
  "eventTitle": "6june",
  "ReservedExternally": 10,
  "eventCategory": "647f1234567890abcdef1234",
  "shortdesc": "A vibrant celebration of music and arts.",
  "longdesc": "Join us for three days of incredible live performances, local food stalls, and art installations.",
  "posterImage": [
    "https://example.com/poster1.jpg"
  ],
  "venueName": "Central Park Arena",
  "venueAddress": {
    "latitude": 40.785091,
    "longitude": -73.968285,
    "address": "5th Ave",
    "city": "New York",
    "state": "NY",
    "country": "USA",
    "zipcode": "10024"
  },
  "startDate": "2026-07-15T18:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2026-07-18T23:00:00.000Z",
  "startTime": "18:00",
  "endTime": "23:00",
  "timeZone": "EST",
  "tickets": [
    {
      "ticketName": "General Admission",
      "ticketShortDesc": "Access to all general stages and food court.",
      "price": 49.99,
      "qty": 500,
      "salesStart": "2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z",
      "salesEnd": "2026-07-14T23:59:59.000Z"
    },
    {
      "ticketName": "VIP Experience",
      "ticketShortDesc": "VIP front row seating, free drinks, and private lounge access.",
      "price": 149.99,
      "qty": 50,
      "salesStart": "2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z",
      "salesEnd": "2026-07-14T23:59:59.000Z"
    }
  ],
  "refundPolicy": "1 Day Before",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "ageRestriction": "18+",
  "showAttendees": true,
  "dressCode": "Casual Summer",
  "fetcherEvent": false
}


### 3. Update an Event (Draft or Published)
@eventId = 6a2904739f3feca6e22f4f62
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/edit/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  # "eventTitle": "Summer Music Festival 2026 (Updated)",
  # "shortdesc": "An updated vibrant celebration of music and arts.",
  "ReservedExternally": 15
}


### 4. Publish a Draft Event (Transition from Draft to Published)
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/edit/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": false,
  "eventTitle": "Tech Conference 2026",
  "eventCategory": "647f1234567890abcdef1234",
  "shortdesc": "A major technology conference.",
  "longdesc": "Join industry leaders for talks, panels, and workshops.",
  "posterImage": ["https://example.com/tech_poster.jpg"],
  "venueName": "Convention Center",
  "venueAddress": {
    "latitude": 37.7749,
    "longitude": -122.4194,
    "address": "Market St",
    "city": "San Francisco",
    "state": "CA",
    "country": "USA",
    "zipcode": "94103"
  },
  "startDate": "2026-08-20T09:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2026-08-22T17:00:00.000Z",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00",
  "timeZone": "PST",
  "tickets": [
    {
      "ticketName": "General Admission",
      "price": 99.99,
      "qty": 200
    }
  ]
}


### 5. Invalid: Try to revert a published event back to draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/edit/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": true
}


### 6. Invalid: Try to set end date in the past
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/edit/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endDate": "2020-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

#======================================= ==== FILTER ==== ==============================================

### 7. List Events - Standard Retrieve (Active/Upcoming Events)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?userId=6a1e80665979beee41cf5f4b&page=1&limit=10&filter=organizer&status=Past
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 8. List Events - Filter by Status (Explicitly show Cancelled, Live, or Past events)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?status=Cancelled
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 9. List Events - Multi-way Filtering (Custom date range + Category + Search + Status combined)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?fromDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&toDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z&categoryId=647f1234567890abcdef1234&search=Music&status=Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 10. List Events - Time Slot Presets (Happenings Soon, This Month, Today, This Weekend, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?filter=happeningsoon,thismonth
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 11. List Events - Time of Day Slot Filter (Morning, Afternoon, Evening)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?timeOfDay=morning,afternoon
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 12. List Events - Geospatial Distance Search (Radius of 50km from Lat/Lng coordinates)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?latitude=40.785091&longitude=-73.968285&radius=50
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 13. List Events - Viewport Bounding Box Map Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?north=40.800000&south=40.700000&east=-73.900000&west=-74.000000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14. List Events - Organizer Events (Latest Created First)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?filter=organizer
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.a. List Events - Sorted by Latest Created (Public exploration)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?filter=latest
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.b. List Events - Organizer Draft Events Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?filter=organizer,draft
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.c. List Events - Organizer Published Events Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?filter=organizer&isDraft=false
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.d. List Events - Exclude My Created Events (using excludeMyEvents query parameter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?excludeMyEvents=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.e. List Events - Exclude My Created Events (using excludemyevents filter keyword)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?filter=excludemyevents
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.f. List Events - Organizer Events (Live & Upcoming)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/list?page=1&limit=3&filter=organizer&status=Live,Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

#======================================== FILTER ==========================================


### 14. Get Event Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/details/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 15. Cancel an Event (Organizer/Admin cancels event and processes all refunds)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "reason": "Cancelled due to severe weather conditions"
}


### 16. Get Unique Event Attendees List (With Aggregated Ticket details, transaction details & pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/attendees/{{eventId}}?page=1&limit=5&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 17. Get Event Attendees List (Transaction level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 17a. Get Event Attendees List — Paginated, Search by Name or bookingId (single field)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?page=1&limit=5&search=kashyap
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 18. Get Event Attendees Check-in List (Organizer/Staff)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendee/event/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 18a. Get Event Attendees Check-in List — Paginated, Search by Name, bookingId or ticket (single field)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendee/event/{{eventId}}?page=1&limit=5&search=kashyap
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
